metaData.label: VACCINES (Gynaecology OR Urology AND no LUX)

metaData.label: MULTIFRANCHISE (General Medicine OR Pharmacist Other AND no LUX)
metaData.criteriaDescription: ( SPECIALTY_1 equal General Medicine OR SPECIALTY_1 equal Pharmacist Other ) AND brick2 is not equal UG1.WBE.01000

metaData.label: DIABETES (Endocrinology OR Diabetology)
metaData.criteriaDescription: ( SPECIALTY_1 equal Internal Medicine AND SPECIALTY_2 equal Endocrinology ) OR ( SPECIALTY_1 equal Internal Medicine AND SPECIALTY_2 equal Diabetology )

metaData.label: LIPIDS (Cardiology)
metaData.criteriaDescription: ( SPECIALTY_1 equal Internal Medicine AND SPECIALTY_2 equal Cardiology ) OR SPECIALTY_1 equal Cardiology OR ( SPECIALTY_1 equal Medical Assistant AND SPECIALTY_2 equal Cardiology )

metaData.label: VACCINES (Pediatrics AND no LUX)
metaData.criteriaDescription: ( SPECIALTY_1 equal Paediatrics OR ( SPECIALTY_1 equal Medical Assistant AND SPECIALTY_2 equal Paediatrics ) ) AND brick2 is not equal UG1.WBE.01000

metaData.label: VACCINES (Gynaecology OR Urology AND no LUX)
metaData.criteriaDescription: ( SPECIALTY_1 equal Urology OR SPECIALTY_1 equal Obstetrics Gynaecology OR ( SPECIALTY_1 equal Medical Assistant AND SPECIALTY_2 equal Obstetrics Gynaecology ) ) AND brick2 is not equal UG1.WBE.01000
